{"tid":1083570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"98/99年九龍城某間幼稚園(已關閉良久)","createTime":"2019-03-29T16:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T17:27:00.000Z","uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7cb524f8a3eb4f49194d974882e70df7f02a65","tid":1083570,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"1998/1999年<br />\n喺九龍城一間而家已經關閉嘅幼稚園<br />\n有一個<span style=\"color: red;\">小朋友</span>有小小鍾意咗一個性麥嘅「小」朋友<br />\n兩位小朋友之間其實冇乜交集<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小朋友</span>只係知道「小」朋友叫咩名<br />\n同埋笑得幾好睇<br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\">小朋友</span>未讀完幼稚園，就搬屋兼轉校去爛頭島<br />\n並再冇見到「小」朋友<br />\n<br />\n一直記得呢一個名, 有咩意思?<br />\n麥「小」朋友而家係咪要叫做麥「大」朋友<br />\n想八卦佢嘅近況呢個行為會唔會太變態<br />\n<br />\n我叫 廷軒, 係真心膠, 想放低過去短短廿年最無聊嘅回憶<br />\n起底相認也好, 手下留情, 謝<br />\n娟"},{"pid":"fcb1f3b557f19253e52d42d419a58f5a0c97c0f8","tid":1083570,"uid":84043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"<del>良久</del><br />\n十幾年先啱<br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dea36ecf700df6d49d2ebc27f6e57f17820ac3","tid":1083570,"uid":60735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"訓啦"},{"pid":"83e7055b6fa5274c75f3d010bcce0cc43267c930","tid":1083570,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"岸久"}]}